import {Component, OnInit} from '@angular/core'; import {ActivatedRoute} from "@angular/router"; import {PlayerProfilesService} from "./player-profiles.service"; import {PlayerProfileRm} from "./player-profile.rm"; import {FormBuilder, FormControl, FormGroup, Validators} from "@angular/forms"; export class FormDictionary { public dict:{[key: string]: string} = {}; constructor(private formGroup: FormGroup){} public AddFormControl(id: string, formControl: FormControl): void{ formControl.valueChanges.subscribe(v => this.dict[id] = v); this.formGroup.addControl(id, formControl); } }
